{"tid":402163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲港男免費幫海洋公園「哈佬喂」打工！","createTime":"2017-09-16T08:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T18:05:27.000Z","uid":29314,"like":366,"dislike":193,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"8479b68f97c9ed092d6755bfee12b844ab060a62","tid":402163,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"海洋公園「哈囉喂全日祭」今午發生命案。下午2時許，一名20多歲男子在香港仔海洋公園意外受傷昏迷，救護員接報到場將他送院，經搶救後證實不治，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者一行七人趁海洋公園舉辦「哈囉喂全日祭」入場，其間他與另外兩名友人在鬼屋「活埋凶間」遊玩時，意外跌傷頭部昏迷，送院不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢以後可以永遠留係果度嚇人了。"},{"pid":"259718fb39a0f09b86d64d76fe64e9482a46ecf3","tid":402163,"uid":117580,"like":143,"dislike":9,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"口德撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85438befef061f938731ef6e679bc9d8cb9efe22","tid":402163,"uid":18845,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"有真鬼玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68be055d164211bfd3abb1112b595b916d12263e","tid":402163,"uid":57407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:23:40.000Z","msg":"足料猛鬼鬼屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030812ce8071db97dfc5fc0ae9aeb562de418a68","tid":402163,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe06b45314716c4111a8d1a74e1bbfe6b984af7","tid":402163,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>足料猛鬼鬼屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連人工都慳返！"},{"pid":"982474fbda88355749a8e9db6b3feae63c76735a","tid":402163,"uid":14250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"c